            <p>
               <ph id="SaveRecord">Click <uicontrol>Save &amp; Exit</uicontrol> to save the record and return to the list page. Optionally, click <uicontrol>Save &amp; Continue</uicontrol> to save the record and continue on the same page.</ph>
            </p>
