         <li id="SaveItem">
            <p>To save the item, perform any of the following as applicable:</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Click <uicontrol>Save &amp; Exit</uicontrol> to return to the list page.</li>
                  <li>Click <uicontrol>Save &amp; Continue</uicontrol> to save and continue on the same page.</li>
                  <li>Click <uicontrol>Save &amp; Create New</uicontrol> to save the current item and continue creating a new  item.</li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </li>
